GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-shot-dead-after-trying-to-wound-israeli-soldiers-in-west-bank-idf-says/0000018f-003f-d6a0-a9ef-c0bf15990000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡的儿子罕见地要求从维基百科中删除</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-pm-netanyahus-son-asks-to-be-removed-from-wikipedia-in-rare-request/0000018e-ffbf-dc66-a39f-ffbfe8440000</link><description>希伯来语维基百科编辑社区正在讨论阿夫纳·内塔尼亚胡因“缺乏公共利益”而提出的从网站上删除的不同寻常的要求，并引发了政治紧张局势</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 10:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-pm-netanyahus-son-asks-to-be-removed-from-wikipedia-in-rare-request/0000018e-ffbf-dc66-a39f-ffbfe8440000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯之间的谈判陷入困境，但继续满足整个地区的政治利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-talks-are-stuck-but-continue-to-feed-political-interests-across-the-region/0000018e-ffac-d6a0-a9ef-ffbc5ffc0000</link><description>卡塔尔的斡旋导致四名女性人质于10月获释，并于11月签署了首份人质协议，为哈马斯与美国之间提供了开放的渠道。退出调解人角色将对谈判造成沉重打击</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 10:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-talks-are-stuck-but-continue-to-feed-political-interests-across-the-region/0000018e-ffac-d6a0-a9ef-ffbc5ffc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长命令各部委向西岸非法前哨基地提供服务和基础设施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-finance-minister-orders-govt-to-provide-services-to-illegal-west-bank-outposts/0000018e-ff7a-db42-a99f-ffffb08d0000</link><description>贝扎莱·斯莫特里奇 (Bezalel Smotrich) 努力将西岸前哨基地合法化，此前政府在 2024 年前四个月对西岸土地的国有化达到了 25 年来的最高水平</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 07:42:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-finance-minister-orders-govt-to-provide-services-to-illegal-west-bank-outposts/0000018e-ff7a-db42-a99f-ffffb08d0000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，在伊朗局势升级后，甘茨的政党不太可能退出内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/sources-gantzs-party-not-likely-to-quit-netanyahu-govt-following-escalation-with-iran/0000018e-ff29-db42-a99f-ffbf94450000</link><description>以色列战时内阁部长圈内的一位消息人士表示，我们正在尽一切努力充当政府内部的平衡因素。 “在关键点产生最大可能的影响。这不会改变&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 06:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/sources-gantzs-party-not-likely-to-quit-netanyahu-govt-following-escalation-with-iran/0000018e-ff29-db42-a99f-ffbf94450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称两名巴勒斯坦人在试图伤害以色列士兵后被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article-live/palestinian-killed-in-clashes-with-settlers-and-soldiers-in-west-bank/0000018e-fe95-de5a-a9ef-fffd67950000</link><description>一名以色列人在约旦河西岸被埋设的爆炸装置炸伤 ■ 以色列国防军警方正在调查纳布卢斯附近巴勒斯坦救护车司机的死亡事件 ■ 哈尼亚表示，哈马斯愿意在战后加入民族团结政府，坚持要求以色列全面撤军</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 03:21:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article-live/palestinian-killed-in-clashes-with-settlers-and-soldiers-in-west-bank/0000018e-fe95-de5a-a9ef-fffd67950000</guid></item><item><title>尽管以色列反应有限，但与伊朗的现状已被打破</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/despite-israels-limited-response-the-status-quo-with-iran-has-been-breached/0000018e-fd2b-db42-a99f-fdbf3b1d0000</link><description>以色列和伊朗之间的最新一轮袭击凸显了内塔尼亚胡在这一问题上缺乏全面的战略。虽然以色列对结果感到满意，但美国和海湾国家担心地区局势升级</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 03:03:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-21/ty-article/.premium/despite-israels-limited-response-the-status-quo-with-iran-has-been-breached/0000018e-fd2b-db42-a99f-fdbf3b1d0000</guid></item><item><title>上次协议签署五个月后，内塔尼亚胡的举动仍未释放剩余人质</title><l