周五报道称，其中一名死者是恐怖组织“图尔卡尔姆旅”的指挥官穆罕默德·贾比尔</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 19:21:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-says-10-palestinians-eight-soldiers-wounded-in-west-bank/0000018e-fca1-de5a-a9ef-fffdc29a0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，三名真主党成员在黎巴嫩袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/three-hezbollah-members-reportedly-killed-in-lebanon-strike/0000018e-fcaa-d6a0-a9ef-fcbe9bc80000</link><description>阿拉伯电视台报道当天早些时候向以色列发射火箭弹后发生袭击，其中一些火箭弹落在空旷地区</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 18:40:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/three-hezbollah-members-reportedly-killed-in-lebanon-strike/0000018e-fcaa-d6a0-a9ef-fcbe9bc80000</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院通过260亿美元紧急以色列援助，这是自10月7日以来最重要的一步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/u-s-passes-26-billion-in-emergency-israel-aid-most-significant-step-since-oct-7/0000018e-fbdd-db42-a99f-ffffe9760000</link><description>预计参议院也将通过这项法案，该法案遭到 37 名民主党人和 21 名共和党人的反对，一周前伊朗用无人机和导弹袭击了以色列</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 18:01:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/u-s-passes-26-billion-in-emergency-israel-aid-most-significant-step-since-oct-7/0000018e-fbdd-db42-a99f-ffffe9760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 197 天：美国官员称，伊朗发动袭击旨在表明以色列的能力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/iran-strike-intended-to-signal-israels-capabilities-u-s-official-says/0000018e-fc6b-de5a-a9ef-ff7f745d0000</link><description>哈马斯领导人考虑从卡塔尔转移政治基地 ■ 美国官员：以色列周五袭击了保护伊朗核设施的目标地点 ■ 伊拉克军事基地爆炸造成 1 人死亡、8 人受伤 ■ 50 人抗议以色列拘留中心的状况 ■ 这是 197 天后您需要了解的内容战争</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 17:15:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/iran-strike-intended-to-signal-israels-capabilities-u-s-official-says/0000018e-fc6b-de5a-a9ef-ff7f745d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列，在释放人质的示威游行后清理道路后，两名司机被司机杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-killed-by-driver-while-clearing-road-after-demo-for-hostages-release/0000018e-fc2d-d140-a3ee-fcfdafa30000</link><description>哈马斯在加沙扣押的人质家属举行示威活动后，一名警察志愿者和道路维护工人正在搬运物品，结果被一辆偏离道路的SUV撞倒</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 16:30:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-killed-by-driver-while-clearing-road-after-demo-for-hostages-release/0000018e-fc2d-d140-a3ee-fcfdafa30000</guid></item><item><title>“我确信我再也不会走路了。现在我正在为欧洲锦标赛进行训练</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-04-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-was-sure-id-never-walk-again-now-im-practicing-for-the-european-championships/0000018e-edcf-dd51-a79e-ffdf3b6e0000</link><description>自 2019 年成立以来，以色列截肢足球队为失去一条腿的年轻人提供了再次踢球的机会。现在，那些在 10 月 7 日受伤和在战斗中受伤的人已经加入了他们的行列。 “没有什么比能够和他们一起打球更能让我康复了，”新队员 Shaked Biton 说道</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 06:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-04-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-was-sure-id-never-walk-again-now-im-practicing-for-the-european-championships/0000018e-edcf-dd51-a79e-ffdf3b6e0000</guid></item><item><title>正统派对本格维尔的战争是关于权力、金钱和嫉妒的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-war-on-ben-gvir-is-about-power-money-and-jealousy/0000018e-f131-dfe0-a1af-f1fdda740000</link><description>由于对极右翼部长伊塔马尔·本格维尔的政治好战情绪日益不满，内塔尼亚胡联盟内部的冲突加剧</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 06:15:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-20/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-war-on-ben-gvir-is-about-power-money-and-jealousy/0000018e-f131-dfe0-a1af-f1fdda740000</guid></item><item><title>一名巴勒斯坦环卫工人因敢于爬上自家屋顶而被以色列狙击手